official_title: A bill to amend the act of September 19, 1964, authorizing the addition of lands to Morristown National Historical Park in the State of New Jersey, and for other purposes.

summary.text: Increases to 461 acres (previously 281) the land to be procured for the Morristown National Historical Park in New Jersey. Authorizes appropriations of necessary sums to acquire such land. (Amends 16 U.S.C. 409g)
